item.title: Please help with server!
item.dc:creator: @wolfs_goal wolfs goal
item.description:
@wolfs_goal wrote:

ok, first off…

if your using allstar just log onto your server on silabs,

right click a portal…get the object id.

go into client.java

hold down ctrl+f

type in the portal i’d you got off silab

it will show the make global object for it

then it will say the teleblock

then it should say tox: ####
toy: ####

if your using devolution you need to go into config

and open objects.cfg

then put the object in there…

and then it will work
